channel.title: Help webclient Problem
channel.description: Help please, my friend and i made a server. He jarred the client then gave me the link to put into the applet on our site. The Webclient Loads Fine for me and him. Everyone else gets a error loading on the webclient. We are using insanityx client.

item.title: Help webclient Problem
item.dc:creator: @Skiire Skiire
item.description:
@Skiire wrote:

Without that error it’s really hard to give you any advice.

My guess is you compiled it with JDK 7u3 and they’re running it on JDK6u30 or something of the sort.

Like I said until we know that error though you’re just going to get people’s best guesses at the problem.
